\c 20
\s Igunya likaJesu
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngolunye lwalezonsuku\x + Mat. 21.23-27. Mark. 11.27-33.\x*, efundisa abantu ethempelini etshumayela ivangeli, ba\add m\add*fikela abapristi abakhulu lababhali kanye labadala,
\v 2 basebekhuluma laye, besithi: Sitshele, ukuthi izinto lezi uzenza ngaliphi igunya, kumbe ngubani okunike leligunya?
\v 3 Wasephendula wathi kubo: Lami ngizalibuza umbuzo ube munye, njalo lingitshele:
\v 4 Ubhabhathizo lukaJohane lwavela ezulwini, kumbe ebantwini\x + 19.47. Mat. 26.55.\x*?
\v 5 Basebezindlisana, besithi: Uba sisithi: Ezulwini; uzakuthi: Kungani-ke lingamkholwanga?
\v 6 Kodwa uba sisithi: Ebantwini; abantu bonke bazasikhanda ngamatshe\x + Mat. 24.48.\x*; ngoba baleqiniso lokuthi uJohane wayengumprofethi\x + 7.29.\x*.
\v 7 Basebephendula \add ngokuthi\add* kabazi lapho o\add lwa\add*vela khona.
\v 8 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Lami kangilitsheli ukuthi ngenza lezizinto ngaliphi igunya.
\s Umfanekiso wabalimi besivini
\p
\v 9 Waseqala ukutshela abantu lumfanekiso, \add esithi\add*: Umuntu othile wahlanyela isivini, wasiqhatshisa kubalimi\x + Mat. 21.33-46. Mark. 12.1-12.\x*, waya kwelinye ilizwe okwesikhathi eside\x + 8.27.\x*;
\v 10 kwathi ngesikhathi esifaneleyo wathuma inceku kubalimi, ukuze bayinike okwesithelo sesivini; kodwa abalimi bayitshaya ba\add yi\add*thumeza ize.
\v 11 Wasethuma njalo enye inceku; layo bayitshaya ba\add yi\add*yangisa, ba\add yi\add*thumeza ize\x + 20.12. 19.11.\x*.
\v 12 Wasephinda ethuma leyesithathu; layo leyo ba\add yi\add*limaza ba\add yi\add*phosela ngaphandle\x + 20.12. 19.11.\x*.
\v 13 Umninisivini wasesithi: Ngizakwenza njani? Ngizathuma indodana yami ethandekayo; mhlawumbe bebona yona baza\add yi\add*hlonipha.
\v 14 Kodwa abalimi beyibona bazindlisana\x + 3.15.\x*, besithi: Le yindlalifa; wozani, siyibulale, ukuze ilifa libe ngelethu.
\v 15 Bayiphosela ngaphandle kwesivini, ba\add yi\add*bulala. Kambe uzakwenzani kubo umninisivini?
\v 16 Uzakuza, ababhubhise labobalimi, anikele isivini kwabanye. Be\add ku\add*zwa basebesithi: Akungabi\add njalo\x + Roma 3.4,6,31. 6.2,15. 9.14. 11.1,11. 1 Kor.6.15. Gal. 2.17. 3.21. 6.14.\x*\add*!
\v 17 Kodwa wabakhangela wathi\x + 22.61.\x*: Pho kuyini lokhu okulotshiweyo, \add okuthi\add*: Ilitshe abakhi abalalayo, yilo eseliyinhloko yengonsi\x + Hlab. 118.22.\x*?
\v 18 Wonke owela phezu kwalelolitshe, uzaphahlazwa; kodwa loba ngubani eliwela phezu kwakhe, lizamchoboza.
\s Umthelo kaKesari
\p
\v 19 Abapristi abakhulu lababhali basebedinga ukumbamba ngezandla ngalelohola, kodwa besaba abantu; ngoba baqedisisa ukuthi wayekhuluma lumfanekiso emelane labo\x + 19.47.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Basebe\add m\add*qaphela\x + Mat. 22.15-33. Mark. 12.13-27.\x*, bethuma\x + 14.1.\x* inhloli\x + 14.1.\x*, ezazitshaya ezilungileyo, ukuze bambambe ekukhulumeni\x + 20.26.\x*, ukuze bamnikele egunyeni lemandleni\x + 12.11.\x* ombusi\x + Mat. 27.2. Luka 3.1. 23.1.\x*.
\v 21 Bambuza-ke, besithi: Mfundisi, siyazi ukuthi wena ukhuluma ufundise ngokuqondileyo, kawemukeli buso, kodwa ufundisa indlela kaNkulunkulu ngeqiniso\x + Mark. 12.14,32.\x*.
\v 22 Sivunyelwe yini ukuthela kuKesari, kumbe hatshi\x + 23.2. Roma 13.6,7.\x*?
\v 23 Kodwa wabubona ubuqili babo\x + 1 Kor. 3.19. 2 Kor. 4.2. 11.3. Efe. 4.14. 2 Kor. 12.16.\x*, wathi kubo: Lingilingelani?
\v 24 Ngitshengisani \w udenariyo\w**; ulomfanekiso lombhalo kabani? Basebephendula besithi: OkaKesari.
\v 25 Wasesithi kubo: Ngakho nikani uKesari okukaKesari, loNkulunkulu okukaNkulunkulu.
\v 26 Basebesehluleka ukumbamba ngelizwi \add lakhe\add* phambi kwabantu; basebemangaliswa yimpendulo yakhe, bathula\x + 20.20.\x*.
\s Ukuvuka kwabafileyo
\p
\v 27 Kwasekusiza kuye abathile babaSadusi, abaphika besithi kakukho ukuvuka \add kwabafileyo\add*, bambuza,
\v 28 besithi: Mfundisi, uMozisi wasibhalela \add ukuthi\add*: Uba kusifa umfowabo womuntu elomkakhe, lo abesesifa engelamntwana, umfowabo kamthathe umfazi, abesemvusela inzalo umfowabo\x + Dute. 25.5.\x*.
\v 29 Ngakho kwakulezelamani eziyisikhombisa; owokuqala wasethatha umfazi, wafa engelamntwana;
\v 30 lowesibili wamthatha umfazi, laye lo wafa engelamntwana;
\v 31 lowesithathu wamthatha. Kwaba njalo-ke lakwabayisikhombisa; abatshiyanga abantwana, bafa.
\v 32 Ekucineni kwabo bonke kwafa lomfazi.
\v 33 Ngakho ekuvukeni \add kwabafileyo\add*, uzafika abe ngumkabani kubo? Ngoba abayisikhombisa babelaye engumkabo.
\p
\v 34 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Abantwana balumhlaba bayathatha, bendiswe;
\v 35 kodwa labo okuzathiwa bafanele ukuzuza lowomhlaba lokuvuka kwabafileyo kabathathani, kabendiswa\x + 21.36. Seb. 5.41. 2 Thes. 1.5.\x*;
\v 36 ngoba bengelakuphinda bafe; ngoba banjengezingilosi, njalo bangabantwana bakaNkulunkulu, bengabantwana bokuvuka\x + Roma 8.23.\x*.
\v 37 Kodwa ukuthi abafileyo bayavuswa, loMozisi wakutshengisa esihlahleni\x + Mark. 12.26.\x*, lapho eyibiza iNkosi \add ngokuthi\add* nguNkulunkulu kaAbrahama loNkulunkulu kaIsaka loNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + Eks. 3.6.\x*.
\v 38 Futhi kayisuye uNkulunkulu wabafileyo, kodwa owabaphilayo; ngoba bonke baphilela yena\x + Roma 6.10,11. Gal. 2.19.\x*.
\p
\v 39 Abathile bababhali basebephendula bathi: Mfundisi, ukhulume kuhle\x + Mat. 22.34. Mark. 12.28.\x*.
\v 40 Njalo kababanga lesibindi sokuphinda bambuze ulutho\x + Mat. 22.46. Mark. 12.34.\x*.
\s UKristu losendo lwakhe
\p
\v 41 Wasesithi kubo: Batsho njani ukuthi uKristu uyiNdodana kaDavida\x + Mat. 22.41-45. Mark. 12.35-37.\x*?
\v 42 Ngoba uDavida uqobo lwakhe uthi encwadini yeziHlabelelo: INkosi yathi eNkosini yami: Hlala ngakwesokunene sami,
\v 43 ngize ngenze izitha zakho zibe yisenabelo senyawo zakho\x + Hlab. 110.1.\x*.
\v 44 Ngakho uDavida umbiza ngokuthi yiNkosi, pho uyindodana yakhe njani?
\s UJesu usola ababhali
\p
\v 45 Kwathi besalalele abantu bonke, wathi kubafundi bakhe:
\v 46 Xwayani ababhali abathanda ukuhamba bembethe izembatho ezinde, njalo bethanda ukubingelelwa emidangeni\x + Mark. 12.38-40. Mat. 23.5-7. 23.14.\x*, lezihlalo eziqakathekileyo emasinagogeni\x + 11.43.\x*\x + Mat. 23.6. Mark. 12.39.\x*, lezihlalo zabahloniphekayo ezilayelweni;
\v 47 abadla izindlu zabafelokazi, bekhuleka \add isikhathi\add* eside ngokuzenzisa. Laba bazakwemukela ukulahlwa okukhulu\x + 14.7, 8.\x*\x + Mat. 23.6. Mark. 12.39.\x*.